PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION unto Her Majesty whereby the SWAN RIVER FIRST NATION BAND surrenders, for an indefinite term, all of its rights and interests in and to the oil and gas that may be found on certain parts of Swan River Indian Reserve No. 150E in Alberta, for the purpose of granting leases, permits and exploration licences.
Attachments
precis:
Acceptance of a DESIGNATION unto Her Majesty whereby the SWAN RIVER FIRST
NATION BAND surrenders, for an indefinite term, all of its rights and
interests in and to the oil and gas that may be found on certain parts of
Swan River Indian Reserve No. 150E in Alberta, for the purpose of granting
leases, permits and exploration licences.
